<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> September 2024</p><p>At Bill Fanter, we’re committed to providing you with high-quality stock option trading services and educational resources designed to support your financial journey. We deeply value your trust and work hard to ensure that our offerings deliver real value. However, due to the nature of the services we provide, we have implemented a <strong>No Refund Policy</strong>. We kindly ask that you read this policy thoroughly before making a purchase.</p><h2>1. No Refund on Services and Products</h2><p>1.1 <strong>Consultation and Advisory Services</strong><br/>All fees for consultation or advisory services, including one-on-one sessions, are <strong>non-refundable</strong> once the service has been rendered. By purchasing these services, you agree to fully understand that no refund will be provided under any circumstances, including dissatisfaction or perceived lack of results.</p><p>1.2 <strong>Subscription Services</strong><br/>Fees for subscription-based services, including market updates, educational resources, and stock option trading tools, are <strong>non-refundable</strong>. Once a subscription is purchased, it cannot be canceled or refunded, even if you choose to stop using the service before the subscription period ends.</p><p>1.3 <strong>Digital Products and Educational Materials</strong><br/>All sales of digital products, such as eBooks, webinars, and online courses, are <strong>final</strong>. Due to the immediate access granted to these materials, no refunds will be provided after the purchase, regardless of usage or perceived value.</p><h2>2. Non-Refundable Promotions and Discounts</h2><p>Purchases made during promotional periods or using discount codes are subject to the same <strong>No Refund Policy</strong>. Discounts do not alter the non-refundable nature of any products or services purchased from Bill Fanter.</p><h2>3. Market Volatility Disclaimer</h2><p>The stock option trading industry is inherently volatile, and while our services and resources aim to enhance your understanding of the market, we cannot guarantee specific results. Refunds will <strong>not</strong> be provided for any losses incurred in stock option trades or unfavorable market conditions, as these are risks that come with engaging in financial trading.</p><h2>4. No Chargeback Policy</h2><p>By purchasing any service or product from Bill Fanter, you agree to the <strong>No Refund Policy</strong> and waive the right to initiate any chargeback or dispute with your payment provider. Chargebacks or disputes that violate this policy may result in the suspension or termination of your access to our services.</p><h2>5. Amendments</h2><p>Bill Fanter reserves the right to amend this No Refund Policy at any time without prior notice. Any changes will be effective immediately upon being posted on our website. It is your responsibility to review this policy periodically for any updates.</p><h2>6. Contact Information</h2><p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Refund Policy or would like further clarification, please contact us at:</p><ul role="list"><li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:options@billfanter.com">options@billfanter.com</a></li></ul>
